 XTENSION= 'BINTABLE'           / binary table extension                         
 BITPIX  =                    8 / 8-bit bytes                                    
 NAXIS   =                    2 / 2-dimensional binary table                     
 NAXIS1  =                19200 / width of table in bytes                        
 NAXIS2  =                    1 / number of rows in table                        
 PCOUNT  =                    0 / size of special data area                      
